## Full Infrastructure Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph SETUP["One-Time Setup (Sequential)"]
        INIT["/auto-init<br/>Hub or Consumer?<br/>Generate infra.json, repos.json"]
        PROVISION["/auto-provision<br/>(hub only)<br/>Create DynamoDB, SQS, S3,<br/>SNS, IAM, Lambda, API GW"]
        PIPELINES["/auto-pipelines<br/>Import 10 (hub) or 6 (consumer)<br/>pipeline YAMLs + set vars"]
        DEPLOY["/auto-deploy<br/>(hub only)<br/>Package and upload Lambda code"]
        LAMBDA_ENV["/auto-lambda-env<br/>(hub only)<br/>Set ADO PAT, secrets,<br/>pipeline IDs, tag gates"]
        WEBHOOKS["/auto-webhooks<br/>Create ADO service hooks +<br/>PR Review build policy"]
        ALARMS["/auto-alarms<br/>(hub only)<br/>Create 4 CloudWatch alarms +<br/>SNS email subscription"]

        INIT --> PROVISION --> PIPELINES --> DEPLOY --> LAMBDA_ENV --> WEBHOOKS --> ALARMS
    end

    subgraph RUNTIME["Runtime (24/7 Autonomous)"]
        ADO_EVENT["ADO Event<br/>(WI update, PR comment,<br/>PR created)"]
        APIGW["API Gateway<br/>POST /wi or /pr"]
        LAMBDA["Lambda Router<br/>(WI-Router or PR-Router)"]
        DEDUP["DynamoDB dedupe check"]
        RATE["Rate limit check"]
        PIPELINE["ADO Pipeline<br/>Claude Code CLI"]
        AGENT["Agent executes<br/>(review, answer, fix, etc.)"]
        RESULT["Posts to ADO<br/>(comments, PRs, bugs)"]

        ADO_EVENT --> APIGW --> LAMBDA --> DEDUP
        DEDUP -->|new| RATE
        DEDUP -->|duplicate| SKIP1((Skip))
        RATE -->|under limit| PIPELINE
        RATE -->|over limit| SKIP2((Skip))
        PIPELINE --> AGENT --> RESULT
    end

    subgraph MONITOR["Ongoing Operations"]
        DOCTOR["/auto-doctor<br/>Health check"]
        STATUS["/auto-status<br/>DLQ depth, tokens, rates"]
        EVAL["/auto-eval<br/>Test agent quality"]
        TEST["/auto-test<br/>Dry-run against real data"]
    end

    ALARMS --> ADO_EVENT
    RESULT -.-> DOCTOR

    style SETUP fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style RUNTIME fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style MONITOR fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style RESULT fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
```

