## Setup Flow (Hub Profile)

**Developer types:** `/auto-init` then follow sequential steps

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph STEP1["1. /auto-init"]
        Q1["Hub or Consumer?"]
        HUB["full-hub profile"]
        CONS["consumer profile"]
        FILES1["infra.json<br/>repos.json<br/>.env.template"]
        Q1 -->|hub| HUB --> FILES1
        Q1 -->|consumer| CONS --> FILES1
    end

    subgraph STEP2["2. /auto-provision (hub only)"]
        DDB["DynamoDB<br/>3 tables: dedupe,<br/>rate-limits, token-budget"]
        SQS["SQS<br/>Dead-letter queue<br/>(14-day retention)"]
        S3["S3<br/>Agent output bundles<br/>(90-day lifecycle)"]
        SNS["SNS<br/>Alert topic"]
        IAM["IAM<br/>Lambda execution role"]
        LAMBDA_PH["Lambda<br/>2 placeholder functions:<br/>WI-Router, PR-Router"]
        APIGW_R["API Gateway<br/>HTTP API: /wi, /pr routes"]
    end

    subgraph STEP3["3. /auto-pipelines"]
        P1["ado-cli-dor.yml"]
        P2["ado-cli-dod.yml"]
        P3["ado-cli-dod-fix.yml"]
        P4["ado-cli-pr-review.yml"]
        P5["ado-cli-pr-answer.yml"]
        P6["ado-cli-bug-fix.yml"]
        P7["ado-cli-qa.yml"]
        P8["ado-cli-dev-agent.yml"]
        P9["ado-cli-doc-agent.yml"]
        P10["ado-cli-estimation.yml"]
        VARS["Pipeline variables:<br/>ANTHROPIC_API_KEY<br/>MONTHLY_TOKEN_CAP<br/>LLM_MODEL"]
    end

    subgraph STEP4["4. /auto-deploy (hub only)"]
        PKG["Package wi-router +<br/>pr-router + shared libs"]
        UPLOAD["aws_lambda_deploy<br/>(audit-wrapped)"]
        PKG --> UPLOAD
    end

    subgraph STEP5["5. /auto-lambda-env (hub only)"]
        ENV_VARS["ADO_PAT<br/>WEBHOOK_SECRET<br/>TAG_GATE per agent<br/>Pipeline IDs<br/>PR_ANSWER_PIPELINE_MAP"]
    end

    subgraph STEP6["6. /auto-webhooks"]
        WH_WI["WI hooks - hub only<br/>workitem.updated + tag filter"]
        WH_PR["PR Answer hook - all repos<br/>pullrequest-comment-event<br/>per-repo + per-branch"]
        WH_POLICY["PR Review policy (all)<br/>Build validation on base branch"]
    end

    subgraph STEP7["7. /auto-alarms (hub only)"]
        A1["DLQ depth > 5"]
        A2["WI-Router errors > 3/hr"]
        A3["PR-Router errors > 3/hr"]
        A4["Lambda throttles"]
        SNS_SUB["SNS email subscription"]
    end

    FILES1 --> DDB
    APIGW_R --> P1
    VARS --> PKG
    UPLOAD --> ENV_VARS
    ENV_VARS --> WH_WI
    WH_POLICY --> A1

    style STEP1 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style STEP2 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style STEP3 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style STEP4 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style STEP5 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style STEP6 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
    style STEP7 fill:none,stroke:#90a4ae
```

